skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby boy names
des:
Picking a baby name is hard! Sometimes is just takes hearing the right name to make everything click. 

This skill brings over 2000 baby names and their accompanying origins to you to give you ideas wherever you and Alexa are. Just ask for a boys name and maybe you'll find the one!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
